      • setPathForPartition

        public static long setPathForPartition​(Path path,
                                       int partitionBy,
                                       long timestamp)
        Sets the path to the directory of a partition taking into account the timestamp and the partitioning scheme.
        Parameters:
        path - Set to the root directory for a table, this will be updated to the root directory of the partition
        partitionBy - Partitioning scheme
        timestamp - A timestamp in the partition
        Returns:
        The last timestamp in the partition
